# .dockerignore for viral-reviewer Cloud Run image (P5.2.1)
# Per W3 P5.2 verdict f7d46bb 决策 H (11 categories + vercel.ts 排除).
# Goal: 缩 build context (2GB+ -> ~50MB), 绝禁 secret 进 image.
#
# 排除原则: 任何不被 npm ci / next build / runtime 直接需要的文件全排除.

# -------- Secrets (HIGHEST PRIORITY — NEVER leak into image) --------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.env.docker.local

# -------- Node / build outputs (rebuilt inside container) --------
node_modules
.next
out

# -------- Tests --------
tests
e2e
playwright-report
test-results
coverage
vitest.config.ts
playwright.config.ts

# -------- Docs (不进 runtime) --------
docs
*.md
README.md
PLAN.md
PROGRESS.md
CLAUDE.md

# -------- Data fixtures / user uploads --------
# data/ 大部分文件 build / runtime 需要 (seed/viral-videos.ts build 时 import；
# enriched-cutplans/* + scraped/enriched-*.json + technique-index.json runtime 读)
# 只排除 dev artifacts (大 mp4s + probe outputs + transient logs)
data/raw-mp4s
data/probes
data/enrichment-errors.json
data/rescrape-*.json
data/scraped/tiktok-*.json
data/scraped/instagram-*.json
data/enrich-batch.log
public/uploads
scripts/*.pdf
scripts/sample-*

# -------- Dev scripts (tsx 跑, runtime 不需要) --------
scripts

# -------- Git --------
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# -------- Editor / tool state --------
.claude
.worktrees
.vscode
.idea
.npmrc

# -------- Vercel artifacts (Cloud Run runtime 不读, 防 noise; per W3 verdict H 显式排除) --------
.vercel
.vercelignore
vercel.ts

# -------- Misc build artifacts --------
*.log
*.tsbuildinfo
*.tar
*.zip
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# -------- TLS keys / certs (defense in depth, per security-reviewer LOW finding) --------
# 项目当前无 *.key / *.crt 等，但加排除避免未来意外 commit 混入 image
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.p12
*.pfx

# -------- Dockerfile itself (no recursive build) --------
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml
